<HEADLINE> East China Cooperates Against Fake Goods </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, April 27 (Xinhua) -- This east China municipality and
its six neighboring provinces have formed a cooperative
organization for quality supervision to wage a joint battle
against counterfeit goods
</P>
<P>
The new body was founded here today.
</P>
<P>
The directors of the local technology supervision bureaus
agreed that the new organization will help them crack down on
trans-provincial criminal gangs which specialize in producing
and selling fake products.
</P>
<P>
They underlined that name-brand products should be particularly
well protected. 
</P>
</TEXT>
