Daily" also showed interest in the session, especially on the
drafts of laws concerning higher education and the prevention of
juvenile delinquency under discussion at the session.
</P>
<P>
The group discussion of the NPC Standing Committee members is
normally attended by only Xinhua reporters. But this time many
other press organizations, including the China News Service and
"China Daily," were present.
</P>
<P>
The Xinhua News Agency released more news with a wider range of
news coverage than the previous NPC Standing Committee
sessions.  
