Monday.
</P>
<P>
The CPI data is widely tipped to show inflation remains
subdued, thus increasing speculation of a rate cut by the Reserve
Bank.
</P>
<P>
The Australian dollar also sank slowly at the end of the
trading day, weighed down by the weakness in the Japanese yen and
the gold price.
</P>
<P>
