"The yen is still very, very choppy and most things in this time
zone are moving with it."
</P>
<P>
A weakness in the gold price also caused damage to the local
unit.
</P>
<P>
"The fact that gold very easily went back under 310.00 U.S.
dollars has also weighed on the Aussie," Macarounas said.
</P>
