visit will undoubtedly bolster bilateral relations based on
friendly cooperation.
</P>
<P>
"We are highly satisfied with the steady improvement in
Sino-Kyrghyz relations, as well as the deepening of mutual trust
and the development of economic and trade cooperation in recent
years," said Li.
</P>
<P>
Akayev expressed his sincere gratitude for China's unselfish
support of his country, and expressed the hope that the two
nations will strengthen bilateral cooperation in all areas.
</P>
<P>
Akayev arrived in Beijing on Sunday for a five-day visit at the
invitation of President Jiang Zemin. 
