<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, April 27 (Xinhua) -- Ronnie O'Sullivan beat fellow
Briton Alan McManus 13-4 in the World Snooker Championships in
Sheffield on Monday and will meet Jimmy White in the
quarter-finals.
</P>
<P>
