champion and fellow Briton Ken Doherty after beating Mark King
13-9.
</P>
<P>
Briton Peter Ebdon's return to form continued as he dismissed
Fergal O'Brien of Ireland 13-5 for a place in the last eight
against compatriot Mark Williams. 
